snippet.title: 3DO - PS2 - 24/7 - Portal Runner Trailer
snippet.description: Early video of the PS2 version of Portal Runner, an Army Men spinoff from a 3DO demo disc given away with new PS2's bought in Game stores in the UK. DVD is dated 4th February 2001. I haven't done anything to the footage, that's how it looks on the disc.
